    LORE_RELIC_OLDLODGE_KEY = [[
The Oldlodge Key does not belong to any door still standing. It ...the day the new lodge opened its doors and the old one fell quiet.

It should have gone to a wall or a drawer, but instead it began t... keep eyes peeled for doors that do not like being watched closely.

